cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM. 

The paper deals with visual question answering (VQA) in images, which involves computer vision (CV) and natural language processing (NLP) techniques. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a novel method for domain adaptation, which falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with multiple modalities (i.e., images, questions, and answers), which is related to multimedia (cs.MM).
